        "readme": {
          "childMarkdownRemark": {
            "html": "<h1 id=\"gatsby-theme-weather\"><a href=\"#gatsby-theme-weather\" aria-label=\"gatsby theme weather permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-theme-weather</h1>\n<p>A weather dashboard <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/themes/\">Gatsby theme</a>, composed using <a href=\"https://mdxjs.com/\">MDX</a> and <a href=\"https://theme-ui.com/\">Theme UI</a>, powered by <a href=\"https://darksky.net/dev\">Dark Sky</a>.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/josefaidt/gatsby-theme-weather\">\n    <img alt=\"gatsby-theme-weather screenshot\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/josefaidt/gatsby-theme-weather/master/images/screenshot-0.0.3.png\" width=\"1000\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n<h2 id=\"features\"><a href=\"#features\" aria-label=\"features permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>MDX composition with custom shortcodes</li>\n<li>Theme UI-based theming</li>\n<li>Geolocation-provided weather</li>\n<li>Weather context state hook available for custom components - <code class=\"language-text\">useWeather</code></li>\n<li>Refresh interval for data fetching</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"installation\"><a href=\"#installation\" aria-label=\"installation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<p>To use this theme in your Gatsby sites, follow these instructions:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Install the theme</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">yarn add gatsby-theme-weather</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add the theme to your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n     resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-theme-weather'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n     options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n       apiKey<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> process<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>env<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">API_KEY</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n     <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Install <code class=\"language-text\">dotenv</code> to keep your API key a secret</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">yarn add -D dotenv</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>Sign up for an API key with <a href=\"https://darksky.net/dev\">Dark Sky</a> to successfully fetch weather data.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create and populate ENV file, <code class=\"language-text\">.env.development</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">API_KEY=your-api-key-here</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Dynamically load ENV file based on <code class=\"language-text\">NODE_ENV</code> (*Note: this is automatically set to <code class=\"language-text\">development</code> by Gatsby in development mode*)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> d <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'dotenv'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>process<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>env<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">NODE_ENV</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> <span class=\"token string\">'PRODUCTION'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">config</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   path<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">.env.development</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n     resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-theme-weather'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n     options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n       apiKey<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> process<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>env<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">API_KEY</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n     <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Start your site</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">gatsby develop</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"deploying\"><a href=\"#deploying\" aria-label=\"deploying permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Deploying</h2>\n<p>In the context of production deployments, ensure the <code class=\"language-text\">API_KEY</code> environment variable is appropriately set.</p>\n<h2 id=\"customization\"><a href=\"#customization\" aria-label=\"customization permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Customization</h2>\n<p>Each piece in this theme is customizable, however it is important to note the <code class=\"language-text\">Skeleton</code> will be our core data layer component and should not be shadowed without careful consideration. Please refer to the Theme UI container styles to modify styles of our other core components (Header, Footer, Main, Container, etc.).</p>\n<h3 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" aria-label=\"options permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Options</h3>\n<p>This theme accepts a few options for functionality, as well as modifying the experience.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Value Type</th>\n<th>Default Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">apiKey</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">String</code></td>\n<td>n/a</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">refreshInterval</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">Integer</code></td>\n<td>20</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><em>Note: <code class=\"language-text\">refreshInterval</code> is expressed in minutes</em></p>\n<h3 id=\"components\"><a href=\"#components\" aria-label=\"components permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Components</h3>\n<p>Below is a table of available components to shadow and use as shortcodes in MDX.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Filename</th>\n<th>Component Name</th>\n<th>Type</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">ColorSwatch.js</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">ColorSwatch</code></td>\n<td>Card component</td>\n<td>Displays current color palette</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">CurrentWeather.js</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">CurrentWeather</code></td>\n<td>Card component</td>\n<td>Displays current weather in a card</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">CurrentTime.js</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">CurrentTime</code></td>\n<td>Time component</td>\n<td>Displays current time (12-hour, 2-digit minute format)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">w-icon.js</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">WIcon</code></td>\n<td>Icon component</td>\n<td>Used to retrieve appropriate icon based on <code class=\"language-text\">props.icon</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">Card.js</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">Card</code> <code class=\"language-text\">{ StyledCard }</code></td>\n<td>Card component</td>\n<td>Base card and named <code class=\"language-text\">StyledCard</code> export for wrapping</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"theme\"><a href=\"#theme\" aria-label=\"theme permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Theme</h3>\n<p>This theme uses Theme UI for MDX. To customize the color palette, shadow the Theme UI configuration file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// src/gatsby-plugin-theme-ui/index.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    text<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#273242'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    background<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#FDF8F7'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    muted<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#A09D9E'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    secondary<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#EFBDB0'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    primary<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#c6797e'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    accent<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#E3F0E5'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"license\"><a href=\"#license\" aria-label=\"license permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>License</h2>\n<p>MIT</p>",
